title: 30 Min CALISTHENICS FULL BODY WORKOUT | Day 2
description:
Follow along with this 30 minute full body Calisthenics workout you can do at home with no equipment. Gain muscle, increase strength and develop flexibility with the Calisthenics exercises included in this routine. This beginner friendly workout has difficulty variations included as well as technique tips throughout.
